name: 透
text:
窓っていうか、なんだろう……
窓の外？
trans:
When I say the window, I mean, um...
Outside the window?

text:
雨降るって
言ってたけど
trans:
Y'know, they were
saying it'd rain.

name: 透
trans: Though I guess they sure are.

name: 透
trans: Not... really, I was just thinking...

name: 透
text:
明るいなーとか、
家だなーとか
trans:
Like "it sure is bright out", or,
"those sure are houses", or.

name: 透
text:
え、今日？
そうなんだ

name: プロデューサー
text: （うっ……しまった。別のことを言えば良かったな……）
trans: (Ah... I should've said something else instead...)
